{"tid":2454372,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"嚴正否認Tesla電動車在中國當間諜　Elon Musk：若有會關門大吉","createTime":"2021-03-20T07:51:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T06:30:39.000Z","uid":28765,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"be6d6cbe4e9878744f4326f13b63811e8ec2c357","tid":2454372,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T07:51:56.000Z","msg":"電動車製造商特斯拉（TESLA）執行長馬斯克（Elon Musk）今利用向中國聽眾發表演說的機會，嚴正否認特斯拉曾把電動車技術用於從事間諜活動。馬斯克表示，如果特斯拉電動車在中國和其他地區從事間諜活動，特斯拉面臨被迫歇業的命運。<br />\n<br />\n馬斯克在中國發展高層論壇上就「下一個顛覆性創新」議題發言時表示，明確涉及間諜活動對商業企業的負面影響很大。馬斯克說：「如果特斯拉把車用於在中國─或其他地區和任何國家─從事間諜活動，我們在所有地區都會被迫歇業（shut down），我們把所有資訊保密到家的動機很強。」<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20210320/BWNOCZT2DZCXLNMHO3GH6MXCP4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20210320%2FBWNOCZT2DZCXLNMHO3GH6MXCP4%2F&d=Msg9JqZwuY5xVY%2FdQIJkDBVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=5a653a83\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20210320%2FBWNOCZT2DZCXLNMHO3GH6MXCP4%2F&h=61082de6\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20210320/BWNOCZT2DZCXLNMHO3GH6MXCP4/</a>"},{"pid":"bf40483daeb6ad931575fd59f17b017caa07a6bc","tid":2454372,"uid":20279,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T07:59:07.000Z","msg":"有咩資料好偷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"922cbf6ec0d9e2d3d52b696114820e2e2c005f7c","tid":2454372,"uid":14494,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T08:00:09.000Z","msg":"咁撚多衛星 要用地面d車個相機偷你資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fa71d31bc66a539b34ccc3314b7af0bcf6d54f5","tid":2454372,"uid":156121,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T08:02:47.000Z","msg":"SpaceX 要搞間諜 可以射任何衛星上太空 仲快同平過你派人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=